# Privacy Policy — Mi PrayList

Last updated: February 2026

Mi PrayList (“we”, “our”, “us”) respects your privacy. This policy explains what data we collect, how we use it, and your choices.

## 1. Data We Collect

### a) Data you provide
- Prayer intention text, notes, and custom content
- Custom books and reading plan setup
- Optional account data (if you sign in), such as email and profile name

### b) App usage data (optional consent)
If you accept measurement permission, we may collect anonymous usage/conversion events for product improvement and ads measurement.

### c) Purchases
In-app purchase status (Premium) is handled through Apple’s StoreKit. We do not receive your full payment card data.

## 2. How We Use Data
- Provide core app features (reading plans, prayer intentions, reminders, history)
- Sync account/profile settings when enabled
- Verify premium access and restore purchases
- Improve app quality and reliability
- Measure feature usage (only when consent is granted where required)

## 3. Sharing of Data
We do not sell personal data.  
We may use service providers strictly to operate app functionality (for example, Apple services and optional backend infrastructure).

## 4. Tracking and Ads Measurement
If shown, tracking/measurement permissions are optional. You can continue using the app even if you decline.

## 5. Data Retention
We keep data only as long as needed to provide app functionality or comply with legal obligations. You can delete app data by deleting content in-app and/or uninstalling the app.

## 6. Your Choices
You can:
- Edit or delete your plans, intentions, and notes in-app
- Disable optional permissions in iOS Settings
- Contact us to request data-related support

## 7. Children
Mi PrayList is not directed to children under 13. If you believe a child submitted personal data, contact us and we will review.

## 8. Security
We use reasonable technical and organizational safeguards, but no method of storage/transmission is 100% secure.

## 9. International Users
Data may be processed in countries different from your location, subject to applicable safeguards.

## 10. Changes to This Policy
We may update this policy. Material updates will be reflected by the “Last updated” date.

## 11. Contact
For privacy questions:

- Email: privacy@mipraylist.com
